snippet.title: "Johnny Is The Victim Not Amber" Sia Speaks on Johnny Depp(IG LIVE)
snippet.description:
"Johnny Is The Victim Not Amber" Sia Speaks on Johnny Depp(IG LIVE) 
If you’ve heard the songs: “cheap thrills” and “Chandelier,” then you’re probably already familiar with the Australian-American singer: Sia. It was very recently that Sia decided to weigh in about the ongoing feud and legal matter between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. On a rare celebrity moment, Sia left no stone unturned in backing Johnny Depp and speaking up against Amber Heard. So, what led Sia to such a conclusion, and what exactly has she said about all this? Let’s find that, shall we?

Here on Film Streak we are all about the latest spill in Hollywood! You can rest assure that we will bring you all the latest celebrity drama and gossip especially concerning you favorite actors! We´ll also make sure to keep you updated on the newest movie updates and releases – so if you are interested in anything that happens in Hollywood, you should make sure to stay tuned!  

And there you have it guys! We hope you enjoyed the video! If you did please consider leaving a like and telling us what you though in the comments!
